    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# 从日志中检测XSS攻击（反射型+存储型的投递阶段）\ngrep -iE '(<script|javascript:|onerror=|onload=|onclick=|alert\\\\(|document\\\\.cookie|img src=x)' access.log\n\n# 检测编码绕过的XSS（URL编码/十六进制编码）\ngrep -iE '(%3Cscript|%3Cimg|\\\\x3cscript|\\\\u003cscript)' access.log","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# 检测SSRF攻击\ngrep -iE '(127\\\\.0\\\\.0\\\\.1|10\\\\.[0-9]+\\\\.[0-9]+\\\\.[0-9]+|172\\\\.(1[6-9]|2[0-9]|3[0-1])\\\\.|192\\\\.168\\\\.|169\\\\.254\\\\.169\\\\.254|file:///|gopher://|dict://)' access.log","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"- <script>     最经典的 XSS 标签\n- <img         图片标签可以嵌入 onerror 等事件来执行脚本\n- <svg         SVG 标签也可以嵌入脚本\n- onerror=     当加载失败时执行代码\n- onload=      当加载成功时执行代码\n- javascript:  伪协议执行 JS\n- <iframe      内嵌框架可加载恶意页面","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# 在 Nginx 日志中搜索常见的 XSS 特征\ngrep -iE '<script|<img|<svg|onerror=|onload=|javascript:' access.log","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"}
