    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"grep \"攻击关键字\" access.log | awk '{print $1}' | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr\ntail -f access.log | grep --line-buffered \"UNION SELECT\"","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"grep \"UNION SELECT\" access.log | awk '{print $1}' | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr\ntail -f access.log | grep --line-buffered \"攻击关键字\"","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# 1. 检查最近1小时内登录失败记录\ngrep \"Failed password\" /var/log/auth.log | wc -l\n\n# 2. 检查最近1小时内sudo使用记录\ngrep \"sudo\" /var/log/auth.log | tail -20\n\n# 3. 检查异常的大文件\nfind / -type f -size +100M -mtime -1 2>/dev/null\n\n# 4. 检查异常的网络连接\nnetstat -tunap | grep ESTABLISHED | grep -v \"127.0.0.1\"\n\n# 5. 检查最近修改的文件\nfind /etc /var/www -type f -mtime -1 2>/dev/null\n\n# 6. 检查crontab是否有新增\ncrontab -l | grep -v \"^#\"\n\n# 7. 检查正在运行的进程\nps aux | grep -E \"(nc|bash.*-i|python.*socket|perl.*socket)\"\n\n# 8. 检查最近1小时的Web访问错误\ntail -1000 /var/log/nginx/access.log | grep -c \" 4[0-9][0-9] \"\ntail -1000 /var/log/nginx/access.log | grep -c \" 5[0-9][0-9] \"","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"},    {"title":"代码示例","language":"bash","code":"# Day XX 学习笔记\n日期：2026年XX月XX日\n\n## 今日核心收获（3点）\n1. \n2. \n3. \n\n## 还没完全理解的（记下来后续查）\n1. \n\n## 明天要复习的内容\n1. \n\n## 顺手记（有用的命令、技巧、链接）","explanation":"护网蓝队代码示例"}
